          "username": "Latonia Greene",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "107637236324100862277",
          "user_review_count": 3,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGso26H8VPUQhiMB7eqiTrkSxJmrMs-eq-Ypp-kIhUx2eSMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "My visit today was amazing. 7am staff called to confirm my appointment. I explained I forgot to order my can right away she assisted. I received my ride to and from hospital. The staff at front desk know my name that feels so good and was very attentive\nTriage always are polite and patient and just adds to making a great day right before seeing the Dr. you can ask questions they always make sure I show and speak to Dr so I can get updated that Dr can advise me about my concerns.\nNow to mention My Dr. Ana Absolutely Amazing Caring great listener Attentive and Supportive\nWalks me though options and when I leave I feel great that she cares\nSo Thxs to Bellevue for having a great staff of service that supports a patient that needs so many services all of this is so important how they speak and treat me",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SS2JFTkhNMjB4VEdZd2FXbFdOM3BJWDJGak9VRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x67a293dafcc5f7e0!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmRKbENHM20xTGYwaWlWN3pIX2FjOUE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "a month ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-05-18T22:53:37+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Jamie Sheller",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "118438870391738985730",
          "user_review_count": 2,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKIrEEdHeAvui7mWyAX9jJ6kft0Z7kgkskFAeupjs2Z1FrJmw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "When I went there, the people were very nice, very quick. There was no time that was wasted. Everything happened so quickly every area that I went to it was on time. Everybody was willing to help everybody spoke to where you could understand it. You didn't need no issues. You didn't need extra people to guide you wrong.  And the experience was great. It wasn't bad, wasn't like other hospitals where you're waiting for 2 to 3  hours just to see somebody when you're on an appointment, when the appointment says they were even earlier to answer me when I got there early and not late and they were really, really great.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205Wk5raFpkRU0wT1ZCM1VVcFhkRGN3U1RsSFIwRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x67a293dafcc5f7e0!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOm9ZNkhZdEM0OVB3UUpXdDcwSTlHR0E%7C%7C?hl=en",
