          "description": "This is absolutely the worst hospital I\u2019ve ever been to in my life! The doctors and nurses have terrible service attitudes and are very uncooperative in communication. Medical efficiency is abysmally low. I was forced to wait for over ten hours. Even when there were no other patients left, we were still made to wait endlessly. No one informed us how long we would have to wait, and patients couldn\u2019t even eat properly. The staff completely ignore patients\u2019 needs, with slow, sluggish and inefficient work. It\u2019s nothing but a waste of money and sheer torture.",
