          "description": "I've been visiting a family member at Bellevue Hospital and it was a difficult experience made worse by the rigidity of visiting hours and many staff who seemed indifferent to visitors already dealing with a stressful situation. The one exception was the ICU team, who were professional, attentive and compassionate throughout. The contrast was stark, and I hope the hospital can bring that same level of care and courtesy to its front-line staff.",
