          "description": "We had a great experience. There\u2019s this staff from dental department who has the same birthday of my daughter she\u2019s very nice and gentle to kids. All medical staff are very accommodating made my daughter feel safe and comfortable. They arranged our future schedule efficiently. Doctor is so kind and so concerned with my daughter\u2019s situation. Educate me and explained me clearly and give me the best advise for my child\u2019s dental treatment. The hospital is clean and well systematic . I highly recommend",
